message.raw:
Wrote a test case for AO/DO classes and fixed some bugs.
It all works I think, except for clicking a combobox with a model, which locks up the entire application.
Bug is not related to my code as far as I can see (disabled all signals, no recursive behaviour)
Well investigate further...
